Preheat oven to 250 degrees F. Melt margarine in 13 x 9 x 2-inch pan in oven. Remove from oven. Stir in onion salt, cayenne pepper, barbecue sauce and vinegar. Add KELLOGG'S CRISPIX cereal, melba toast rounds and pecan halves. Mix until coated. Return to oven and bake for 45 minutes, stirring every 15 minutes. Spread on paper towel to cool.